      "text": "そうでした。その方がコントロールが安定しますし\n次の球は、ふわっといきます！",
      "startTime": 40.4461888473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "よし、三振だ。いいぞー、さくら",
      "startTime": 45.1128552597,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
