      "text": "ああっ、みんなごめん！\n打たれちゃった……",
      "startTime": 52.5686357816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（さくら達が1対0で勝ち越しているけど）\n（最後のイニングでツーアウト満塁か……マズいな）",
      "startTime": 57.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
